#: ../../language/error_codes/E4188.md:1
msgid "E4188"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4188.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `async_with_error_poly`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4188.md:5
msgid "`async` functions cannot use error polymorphism."
msgstr "`async` 函数不能使用错误多态。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4188.md:7
msgid ""
"MoonBit currently does not support combining `async` with `raise?`. An "
"`async` function is raising by default, so use an ordinary `async fn` "
"when the function may raise, or remove `async` if the function is not "
"asynchronous."
msgstr ""
"MoonBit 目前不支持将 `async` 与 `raise?` 结合使用。`async` "
"函数默认可能抛出错误，因此当函数可能抛错时请使用普通的 `async fn`；如果函数并不需要异步行为，则移除 `async`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4188.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4188.md:13
msgid "The following function combines `async` with `raise?`:"
msgstr "下面的函数同时使用了 `async` 和 `raise?`："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4188.md:15
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"async fn load() -> Unit raise? {\n"
"  ()\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  ignore(load)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4188.md:19
msgid "MoonBit will report an error."
msgstr "MoonBit 会报告一个错误。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4188.md:21
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4188.md:23
msgid ""
"Remove `raise?` from the async function, or remove `async` if the "
"function does not need asynchronous behavior:"
msgstr "从异步函数中移除 `raise?`；如果函数不需要异步行为，则移除 `async`："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4188.md:26
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"fn load() -> Unit {\n"
"  ()\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  ignore(load)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
